attributes.title: This is what a $1,000,000 house looks like.
attributes.caption: Anyone else used to watch the Price is Right after school? No? My dad used to always say “Watching The Price Is Right is like trying to find a bargain at a garage sale - you never know what treasure you'll uncover or how much you'll end up paying for that slightly used toaster oven”. I miss him…he is not gone or anything, but I haven’t seen him since….never mind, they will never find me, I am safe now, the Bahamas is treating me right…they can’t force me to do social anymore…I am free!
attributes.display_title: S1:E32 - This is what a $1,000,000 house looks like.
